{"tid":1389334,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"不合作運動搞香港人，不如去玩鳩嗚仲好","createTime":"2019-07-31T01:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:43:14.000Z","uid":27415,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd29ad35c94c142859d4b2b2ad839fac8643eeee","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:24:43.000Z","msg":"屌 次次經過尖沙嘴，見到班鄉村大陸西如常購物，完全不受影響咁，好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該重點招呼尖沙嘴，等班仆街唔敢黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83bcad1092df885e10667802ac940c6d69c3169","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:26:06.000Z","msg":"個班大陸西咁鍾意係名店門口排隊，緊係跟住一齊排，係佢地後面叫口號，唱歌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係佢地一生中，最昂貴最缺少既唔係佢排緊隊買個D奢侈品，係「自由」啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be8ee919caf5a99f9deb4e5b21a84b7c4b37f29","tid":1389334,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n光復紅土個日應該要搞搞佢地<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/31/092607_244807646daf654d1f7de97737d40574.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F31%2F092607_244807646daf654d1f7de97737d40574.png&h=5836a6c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd31db3347fa4440b4e4660b30e158d245e28f4f","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"一日香港零售業（and飲食業）養住咁多靠大陸西搵食既從業員，一日佢地都唔會槍口對外 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9b422a6105726fa231fd32856eb966773c37ae","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"而且大陸封鎖消息，好多黎香港既大陸西係唔知道發生乜事。<br />\n<br />\n你去佢行街個到同佢一齊行街，做鳩嗚旅伴，佢地就會返去有排講，「遍地開花」啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07336a7167fce5bebc7794c13b8904ea7f4ef55","tid":1389334,"uid":129835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"對準黑警啦,屌你"},{"pid":"44a52dd153ae3dab5258e35c968cd15493168297","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd31db3347fa4440b4e4660b30e158d245e28f4f","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"一日香港零售業（and飲食業）養住咁多靠大陸西搵食既從業員，一日佢地都唔會槍口對外 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"香港呢個社會最大問題係，宜家好多人靠D大陸西既錢黎屌命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家發唔發覺少左好多保險仔煩自己？<br />\n<br />\n因為宜家保險係一車車咁車D保險仔上大陸到拉客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個D「XX冰室」系列，多數招呼大陸人多過香港人，尤其遊客區個D。<br />\n<br />\n海港城呢D高級奢侈品林立既商場更加唔洗講啦，<br />\n每個蝗蟲一定要去朝聖既聖地添啦。"},{"pid":"dfa0a4265c7e9bb9fcea21b866c58721e4ab7dac","tid":1389334,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"樓下有人以死控訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389329</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n人命 快推 附近有冇人勸到"},{"pid":"dfe56763dbcfe2ec2d05f0cf830e482920ed49fd","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"點解我地香港人搞到咁折墮，係自己地方都要去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係死就點都同大陸西攬炒，或者大陸西自己精精地死返上去佢地個「萎大的蛆国」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fb137b4ea011fcbb9e4ec47f3bed7200dd8fe1","tid":1389334,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}